node.text:
In ‘Fashionscapes,’ @ecoage founder @liviafirth digs deep into the impact of diamond mining in Botswana—discovering how the industry emphasizes long-term investment in community, environmental sustainability, and empowers women at all levels.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
To learn more, watch the full film on IGTV & visit the link in bio.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
#NaturalDiamonds #RealisRare⁣⁣⁣

node.text: Choosing a wedding band can be overwhelming thanks to the infinite styles out there. Should it stack with your engagement ring? 💍Should it match your partner's ring? There's no wrong answer here, but we've put together a guide to help you at the link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Only Natural Diamonds on August 06, 2021 tagging @priyankachopra, and @lorraineschwartz. May be a closeup of 1 person and jewelry.

node.text: Not not day-dreaming about getting engaged with @priyankachopra's @lorraineschwartz rings from the 2016 Oscars… but which ones?? Head to the link in bio for more of her best looks.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Only Natural Diamonds on August 05, 2021 tagging @vanessahudgens. May be a closeup of 1 person, standing, jewelry and text that says 'il EGNA'.

node.text: Sure we love a classic hoop, but The New Hoop, as seen on @vanessahudgens, is one of our favorite new trends of the year. 💫How big do you like your hoops? Cheerio, Oreo, or rice cake-sized? Tap the link in bio for more on the trend.

node.text: Say hello to the East Kimberley region in Western Australia, known as the source of the world's finest, rarest pink diamonds.💎 Although you can't book your visit just yet, you can still dream up your outback adventure, with a little help from us at the link in bio. 🦘Where is the first stop on your post-pandemic world tour?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Only Natural Diamonds on July 28, 2021 tagging @justinemarjan, and @kristincavallari. May be an image of 1 person, jewelry and text that says 'YSIUM'.

node.text: @kristincavallari’s red carpet look makes for great wedding hair inspiration, no? Celebrity hairstylist @justinemarjan, who created the gorg look, shared her favorite wedding hairstyles and the diamond earrings to pair with them. How would you wear your hair to your wedding? Tap the link in bio for more tips & tricks from Justine.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Only Natural Diamonds on July 27, 2021. May be an image of jewelry.

node.text: The @buccaneers' Super Bowl ring, created by the one and only @jasonofbeverlyhills, features a historic design and plenty of diamonds—319 to be exact. 🏈💎So what makes this ring boundary-breaking and the first of its kind? Share your guesses in the comments, then tap the link in bio to find out.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Only Natural Diamonds on July 27, 2021 tagging @iamhalsey. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: @iamhalsey's cluster ring and drop earrings are full proof that diamonds and pearls can look edgy & cool. How would you wear one of this year's biggest jewelry trends? Share in the comments then tap the link in bio for more.
